<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 12:28:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>即将上任的日本首相石破浩的“亚洲北约”理念对美国外交进行考验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/incoming-japan-pm-ishibas-asian-nato-idea-test-us-diplomacy-2024-09-27/</link><description>被任命为日本下一任首相的石破茂可能会提出让华盛顿陷入“亚洲北约”并在美国领土上驻扎日本军队的提议，从而重塑与东京最密切的联盟，这可能会给美国带来外交上的麻烦。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 11:31:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/incoming-japan-pm-ishibas-asian-nato-idea-test-us-diplomacy-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本称中国海军航母在太平洋停留7天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navy-carrier-spotted-pacific-seven-days-japan-says-2024-09-27/</link><description>日本防卫省周五表示，过去7天在太平洋发现中国海军“辽宁”号航母。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 10:14:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navy-carrier-spotted-pacific-seven-days-japan-says-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国降息和中国刺激措施引发更多亚洲私募股权交易的希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-rate-cut-china-stimulus-spark-hope-more-asia-private-equity-deals-2024-09-27/</link><description>业内人士表示，美国降息和中国对市场的经济刺激计划将有利于亚洲私募股权交易，融资成本降低和市场情绪改善预计将使退出变得更容易。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 10:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-rate-cut-china-stimulus-spark-hope-more-asia-private-equity-deals-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国PCE关注中国加速反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-27/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 10:04:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>印度钢铁制造商集团警告美国征收关税后中国进口量增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-steelmaker-group-warns-rising-chinese-imports-after-us-tariffs-2024-09-27/</link><description>印度主要钢铁制造商组织周五警告称，在美国决定对中国进口钢铁征收25%的关税后，印度从中国的进口将进一步增加。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:54:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-steelmaker-group-warns-rising-chinese-imports-after-us-tariffs-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>对石破茂被选为日本下一任首相的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/reactions-shigeru-ishibas-selection-japans-next-pm-2024-09-27/</link><description>以下是对石破茂当选日本自民党党魁并使其下周接任首相的反应：</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:33:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/reactions-shigeru-ishibas-selection-japans-next-pm-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>舒适达制造商 Haleon 将增持中国合资企业股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sensodyne-maker-haleon-raise-stake-china-jv-2024-09-27/</link><description>英国消费者保健公司 Haleon 周五表示，已同意以 44.7 亿元人民币（6.3735 亿美元）将其在中国合资企业的股份从 55% 增加到 88%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:11:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sensodyne-maker-haleon-raise-stake-china-jv-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>台湾表示期待在石破浩领导下深化与日本的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-it-looks-forward-deepening-ties-with-japan-under-ishiba-2024-09-27/</link><description>赖清德领导的民进党周五表示，台湾总统赖清德期待在石破茂领导下深化与日本执政党的关系。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-it-looks-forward-deepening-ties-with-japan-under-ishiba-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警称菲律宾船只向仁爱礁运送物资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-says-philippine-vessel-took-supplies-second-thomas-shoal-2024-09-27/</link><description>中国海警周五表示，菲律宾派出一艘民用船向仁爱礁的一艘军舰运送日常必需品，北京称这艘军舰在南海有争议的水道上非法“搁浅”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-says-philippine-vessel-took-supplies-second-thomas-shoal-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国数据公布前，欧洲斯托克 600 指数跌破纪录高位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/stoxx-600-hits-record-high-china-driven-rally-set-weekly-gains-2024-09-27/</link><description>欧洲股市从周五早些时候触及的历史高位回落，因美国重要数据公布前市场普遍谨慎，不过盟可睐 (Moncler) 和奢侈品股的上涨限制了价格的进一步下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 07:37:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/stoxx-600-hits-record-high-china-driven-rally-set-weekly-gains-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>即将领导日本的局外人石破茂是谁？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/shigeru-ishiba-outsider-set-lead-japan-2024-09-27/</link><description>这位 67 岁的领导人在四次尝试失败后终于成功。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 06:39:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/shigeru-ishiba-outsider-set-lead-japan-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国9月份工厂活动继续下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-seen-extending-declines-sept-2024-09-27/</link><description>由于国内需求疲软和全球贸易壁垒不断上升继续困扰着世界第二大经济体，中国的工厂活动可能在 9 月份连续第五个月保持收缩。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 06:21:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-seen-extending-declines-sept-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：上海、深圳取消重点购房限制提振市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-shenzhen-lift-key-home-purchase-curbs-boost-market-sources-say-2024-09-27/</link><description>四位知情人士称，中国顶级城市上海和深圳正计划取消剩余的主要购房限制，以吸引潜在买家并提振疲软的房地产市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 06:16:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-shenzhen-lift-key-home-purchase-curbs-boost-market-sources-say-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国海岸警卫队观察阿拉斯加附近俄罗斯和中国海军活动的增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-coast-guard-watching-uptick-russian-chinese-navy-activity-near-alaska-2024-09-27/</link><description>一位高级指挥官周五表示，美国海岸警卫队正在观察中国和俄罗斯海军在阿拉斯加和北太平洋周围的活动“增加”，但迄今为止的遭遇都非常专业。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 05:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-coast-guard-watching-uptick-russian-chinese-navy-activity-near-alaska-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国导弹试验后斐济敦促“尊重我们的地区”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/fiji-urges-respect-our-region-after-china-missile-test-2024-09-27/</link><description>在中国发射洲际弹道导弹后，斐济总统拉图·威廉姆·卡托尼韦雷呼吁“尊重我们的地区”并停止在太平洋进行导弹试验。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 04:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/fiji-urges-respect-our-region-after-china-missile-test-2024-09-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>